{"tid":2429831,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"醫管局員工陣線主席被控違反港區國安法  遭醫管局停職","createTime":"2021-03-02T14:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T14:40:43.000Z","uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ff35f709f4e6ffe7a447d5df06dee4547201d79e","tid":2429831,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"【35+案】員工陣線主席余慧明 被控違反港區國安法  遭醫管局停職<br />\n<br />\n因去年參加民主派初選而被控違反《港區國安法》串謀顛覆國家政權罪，醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明遭醫管局停職。<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局發言人表示，就一名員工被控違反港區國安法，醫管局按既定人力資源程序，會對涉事員工作出停職安排。<br />\n<br />\n資料相片：本台採訪記者<br />\n========================= <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6kVU3L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6kVU3L.jpg&h=cb3f30c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52afd23fc59948ee714198a605d432eb0b977464","tid":2429831,"uid":263648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff35f709f4e6ffe7a447d5df06dee4547201d79e","tid":2429831,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:22:50.000Z","msg":"【35+案】員工陣線主席余慧明 被控違反港區國安法  遭醫管局停職<br />\n<br />\n因去年參加民主派初選而被控違反《港區國安法》串謀顛覆國家政權罪，醫管局員工陣線主席余慧明遭醫管局停職。<br />\n<br />\n醫院管理局發言人表示，就一名員工被控違反港區國安法，醫管局按既定人力資源程序，會對涉事員工作出停職安排。<br />\n<br />\n資料相片：本台採訪記者<br />\n========================= <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6kVU3L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6kVU3L.jpg&h=cb3f30c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:38:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d664b631a701ca40e00b4cc3b7f88221b2010877","tid":2429831,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T14:40:43.000Z","msg":"糧照出<br />\n理得你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}